---
/* no props */
---

<section id="about" class="pt-16 md:pt-32 py-20 bg-white">
  <div
    class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12"
  >
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 reveal">
      <div class="relative">
        <img
          src="/about11.png"
          alt="Rivershore Trading Operations"
          class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl object-cover w-full h-[300px] md:h-[500px]"
        />
        <div
          class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-32 h-32 bg-brand-green/10 rounded-full -z-10"
        >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 reveal">
      <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-brand-green mb-6"></div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-navy mb-6">
        Delivering Industrial Excellence <span class="text-brand-green"
          >Across Qatar</span
        >
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Rivershore Trading delivers unparalleled expertise in industrial supply
        and facility management. We excel in providing tailored solutions for
        residential, commercial, and industrial sectors, ensuring that every
        project is backed by a commitment to quality, safety, and long-term
        reliability.
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-brand-navy font-semibold">
          <span class="text-brand-green">✔</span> Supply: Premium Materials (Electrical,
          Plumbing, HVAC) focused on efficient procurement and international standards.
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-brand-navy font-semibold">
          <span class="text-brand-green">✔</span> Maintenance: Expert Building Maintenance
          and Civil Works, ensuring safety-first operations and cost-effective repair
          solutions.
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-brand-navy font-semibold">
          <span class="text-brand-green">✔</span> Sustainability: Comprehensive Scrap
          Trading for all industrial materials, driving operational excellence through
          responsible waste management.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <a
        href="/about"
        class="inline-block bg-brand-navy text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-brand-navy-dark transition-all"
      >
        Learn More
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
